---
// Hero: headline, sub, CTAs
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="stack-position">
      <span>dlt loads it</span>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>dbt transforms it</span>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span class="dvt-emphasis">dvt visualizes it</span>
    </div>

    <h1>Dashboards as data.</h1>

    <p class="sub">
      dvt is an AI-native, open data viz tool where every dashboard
      is a versioned JSON spec — authored by humans and AI agents alike,
      updated live via API or MCP, and rendered faithfully down to the last pixel.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/#early-access" class="btn-primary">
        Request early access
      </a>
      <a href="https://demo.dvt.dev/builder" class="btn-secondary">
        Open the live builder →
      </a>
      <a href="/vision" class="btn-secondary">
        Read the vision →
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="cta-note">
      The builder runs the spec format in your browser — no signup. Early
      access puts dvt on your own data; we reach out personally to set it up.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0 var(--space-16);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stack-position {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-neutral-400);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--color-neutral-200);
  }

  .dvt-emphasis {
    color: var(--color-brand-navy);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-4xl), 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-neutral-900);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .sub {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-neutral-700);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-neutral-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: 14px var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-brand-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-neutral-700);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 14px var(--space-6);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-neutral-700);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-neutral-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-neutral-400);
    color: var(--color-neutral-950);
  }
</style>
